{"tid":175308,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"身家達$1.5萬億 普京其實有錢過蓋茨？","createTime":"2017-03-27T12:04:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T14:10:38.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d71d7fe4a2bd0798258b1c5121f7d647e9f8cba3","tid":175308,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T12:04:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170221/large/1487654165_f481.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170221%2Flarge%2F1487654165_f481.jpg&h=50af8d9c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n2017-03-26 00:04:55 HKT <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯總統普京掌權近20年，行事一向神秘的他究竟有多少身家，是外界非常關注的問題。他曾公開自己收入，聲稱自己年收入不足100萬港元，但有俄羅斯投資者認為，普京身家高達2,000億美元（1.5萬億港元），是全球首富身家的3倍。 <br />\n<br />\n普京至今入主克里終姆林宮17年，英國《國際商業時報》早前再次提出這個問題，引述前基金經理布勞德（Bill Browder）2015年估計，指普京透過物業、瑞士銀行賬戶處理的股票、對沖基金等，秘密聚積私人財富達2,000億美元。 <br />\n<br />\n布勞德當時指，國家所賺的錢，以及原本用於社會基建的資金，都被普京及同黨挪用。如果數字屬實的話，他的身家將遠遠拋離全球首富蓋茨（Bill Gates）的750億美元（5,850億港元）。 <br />\n<br />\n去年有報道披露普京坐擁58架飛機及直升機、總值50萬美元（390萬港元）的名錶收藏以及20間皇宮，又在俄羅斯西北部瓦爾代湖（Lake Valdai）擁有佔地930公頃的豪宅。 <br />\n<br />\n其中普京旗下最有名的奢侈品之一，就是一架值3,500萬美元（2.7億港元）的超級遊艇「奧林匹亞號」（Olympia），據報這是車路士班主阿巴莫域治（Roman Abramovich）祝賀普京上台的大禮。 <br />\n<br />\n他被稱為歐洲最有錢男人時僅回應說：「垃圾」，力斥對方無中生有抹黑他。普京前年4月公開自己2014年收益，稱自己僅賺11.9萬美元（93萬港元）收入，並持有兩個單位物業，以及一個停車場股份。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170326/56332078\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170326%2F56332078&d=dTdn096UhK%2BcydR5vLM29%2FM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=48d74417\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170326%2F56332078&h=20be9854\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170326/56332078</a>"},{"pid":"7e85574cb1e6aeab1fad9a9ec68cf1e2c546078d","tid":175308,"uid":61506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T12:06:52.000Z","msg":"美國總統都無佢咁大權力<br />\n係中共有得同佢比"},{"pid":"6a83f9a4de1625d293a1921c1558a66e83acfccd","tid":175308,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T12:09:16.000Z","msg":"江澤民多過佢啦"},{"pid":"a496f96525e5044000be199f63dbffb3548f28c5","tid":175308,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T12:10:23.000Z","msg":"去年有報道披露普京坐擁58架飛機及直升機、總值50萬美元（390萬港元）<br />\n<br />\n咁平？"},{"pid":"a461a67ae25d0170aa40af68bdeb4ab91362d430","tid":175308,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T12:10:25.000Z","msg":"習大大轉過頭過埋佢"},{"pid":"7a57c86f8faea93d3059fb82697b96b164c32b06","tid":175308,"uid":25758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T12:11:28.000Z","msg":"普京就算係咪咁有錢都係最有料既領袖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c31232f3b8a2ae5da8521700c3a1f6439a2e6556","tid":175308,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T12:11:28.000Z","msg":"佢銀行嗰啲係美金定俄幣先？"},{"pid":"48c8a0b82e3bf7d8cbe514cdda64027970c2d987","tid":175308,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T12:12:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去年有報道披露普京坐擁58架飛機及直升機、總值50萬美元（390萬港元）<br />\n<br />\n咁平？</blockquote><br />\n雖然報紙佬打得衰 但你都睇清楚先啦唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a210f9c69ad0e7921bef384bf8195514110b604f","tid":175308,"uid":75823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T12:12:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>習大大轉過頭過埋佢</blockquote><br />\n14億支那奴隸價值點止14萬億"},{"pid":"e53c2fdb75b595e943ca3e7d8e59dd311bd7db77","tid":175308,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T12:13:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去年有報道披露普京坐擁58架飛機及直升機、總值50萬美元（390萬港元）<br />\n<br />\n咁平？</blockquote><br />\n毒果妓者水平係咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"